019package com.plotsquared.core.events;
020
021import com.plotsquared.core.player.PlotPlayer;
022import com.plotsquared.core.plot.Plot;
023
024public class PlayerEnterPlotEvent extends PlotPlayerEvent {
025
026    /**
027     * Called when a player leaves a plot.
028     *
029     * @param player Player that entered the plot
030     * @param plot   Plot that was entered
031     */
032    public PlayerEnterPlotEvent(PlotPlayer<?> player, Plot plot) {
033        super(player, plot);
034    }
035
036}
